{"tid":1823850,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"連登先係真on9","createTime":"2020-01-14T04:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T17:22:04.000Z","uid":57221,"like":17,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"71c6f48d1cefa99eb399214a998b7f1e7fa3d325","tid":1823850,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:15:37.000Z","msg":"一踏入2020 成個連登變到好恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1823384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1823384</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原文：<br />\n食藍店就影人大頭 將軍澳呢d黃店沙漠區嘅手足真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下下都要出去其他地方食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n所以將軍澳手足食藍店就冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n1300條傻西我屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n仲咁多人認同 <br />\n<br />\n仆街我唔撚玩啦<br />\n<br />\n今日開始日日食藍店<br />\n<br />\n我就住將軍澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你冇資格屌我<br />\n</span></span><br />\n因為你地認同將軍澳係黃店沙漠<br />\n<br />\n本來都唔想再嘈<br />\n<br />\n你班弱智仔仲拎出嚟講<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母</span></strong>"},{"pid":"83ff5d2aa5391068217a626cf30c4cf6bc4764d5","tid":1823850,"uid":57221,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你班弱智食藍店仲聲大大夾惡<br />\n我屌你老母咩<br />\n其實你食唔食關我撚事<br />\n不過你係都要死出嚟柒<br />\n咁係你自己攞嚟<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n以下為奇文共賞：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3hhPVu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3hhPVu.png&h=64f9acc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UD6FNHa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUD6FNHa.png&h=ca2e946a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"843e22688de9b52fce911a2ed8ad163feea2da6a","tid":1823850,"uid":76690,"like":10,"dislike":3,"scor